name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Auto accepts cookies from any website!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It's a script that identifies the "accept cookies" popup in every website you visit and it accepts automatically, so you don't lose time. 

It works on every website, if a particular one is not working please open a ticket to me, thank you!
